article.description: — Leslie Nkereuwem had 15 points off the bench to lead Longwood to an 82-42 win over American on Friday.
article.headline: Nkereuwem scores 15 to carry Longwood over American 82-42
article.linkText: Nkereuwem scores 15 to carry Longwood over American 82-42
article.story: FARMVILLE, Va. -- — Leslie Nkereuwem had 15 points off the bench to lead Longwood to an 82-42 win over American on Friday. DeShaun Wade had 14 points for Longwood (3-1). Isaiah Wilkins added 11 points. Justin Hill had six assists. Johnny O'Neil had 11 points for the Eagles (2-2).
